English | CBZ | 2 Issues

Mouse Guard: Legends of the Guard v2 #1-2 (of 4)
Publisher:  Archaia
Publication Date:  May 22, 2013 - June 26, 2013

Writers:  Stan Sakai, Nick Tapalansky, Ben Caldwell; Christian Slade, Rick Gleary, and Jemma Salume
Artists:  Stan Sakai, Alex Eckman, Ben Caldwell; Christian Slade, Rick Gleary, and Jemma Salume
Additional Pages:  David Petersen

Mouse Guard: Legends of the Guard v2 #1
The 2011 Eisner Award winner for best anthology is back with a second volume! In the mouse tavern the June Alley Inn, a new round of storytelling begins between the patrons. Their goal is to be declared the best story of the night in hopes of having their outstanding debt to the barmaid forgiven. Legends of the Guard continues the tradition of featuring handpicked artists and storytellers by series creator David Petersen. This issue features Stan Sakai (Usagi Yokimbo), Ben Caldwell (The Dare Detectives!), and the Awakening team of Nick Tapalansky and Alex Eckman-Lawn!

Mouse Guard: Legends of the Guard v2 #2
Cursed ghosts, unrequited love, and dire peril abound as the stories continue in the common room of the June Alley Inn. Legends of the Guard continues the tradition of featuring handpicked artists and storytellers by series creator David Petersen with a full serving of of brilliant new art and epic tales from around the Mouse Kingdom.

Thanks goes to Empire for this release.

